{
  "chapter": 8,
  "chapter_summary": "本章承接前章，蓝水灵与东方亮结伴同行，西行途中在一处山野小店遇见西门燕与其母西门夫人。西门燕刁蛮任性却心地善良，对东方亮一见倾心。西门夫人则端庄稳重、识人颇深。蓝水灵与西门燕因误会起了争执，后在东方亮调解下和解。一行人在途中遭遇武当弃徒鲍一虚、杜成林、钟九胜、余兆兴、齐浩淼的追杀。东方亮与蓝水灵联手对敌，险中求胜。西门燕对东方亮心生爱慕，母女的对话进一步揭示了西门家的过往。",
  "dialogues": [
    {"id":"dlg_08_001","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_yan","speaker_name":"西门燕","listener":"xi_men_fu_ren","listener_name":"西门夫人","tone":"撒娇","text":"娘，我饿了！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":60,"line_end":60,"text":"娘，我饿了！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_002","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_fu_ren","speaker_name":"西门夫人","listener":"xi_men_yan","listener_name":"西门燕","tone":"温柔","text":"燕儿乖，店家马上就来。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":62,"line_end":62,"text":"燕儿乖，店家马上就来。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_003","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_yan","speaker_name":"西门燕","listener":"xi_men_fu_ren","listener_name":"西门夫人","tone":"不耐烦","text":"这破店怎的这样慢！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":64,"line_end":64,"text":"这破店怎的这样慢！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_004","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_fu_ren","speaker_name":"西门夫人","listener":"xi_men_yan","listener_name":"西门燕","tone":"庄重","text":"出门在外，燕儿要懂得忍耐。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":66,"line_end":66,"text":"出门在外，燕儿要懂得忍耐。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_005","chapter":8,"speaker":"lan_shui_ling","speaker_name":"蓝水灵","listener":"dong_fang_liang","listener_name":"东方亮","tone":"惊讶","text":"这位姑娘好标致。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":80,"line_end":80,"text":"这位姑娘好标致。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_006","chapter":8,"speaker":"dong_fang_liang","speaker_name":"东方亮","listener":"lan_shui_ling","listener_name":"蓝水灵","tone":"平淡","text":"是西门家的千金。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":82,"line_end":82,"text":"是西门家的千金。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_007","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_yan","speaker_name":"西门燕","listener":"dong_fang_liang","listener_name":"东方亮","tone":"好奇","text":"这位公子，我怎从未见过你？","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":85,"line_end":85,"text":"这位公子，我怎从未见过你？"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_008","chapter":8,"speaker":"dong_fang_liang","speaker_name":"东方亮","listener":"xi_men_yan","listener_name":"西门燕","tone":"恭敬","text":"在下东方亮，西门姑娘。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":87,"line_end":87,"text":"在下东方亮，西门姑娘。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_009","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_yan","speaker_name":"西门燕","listener":"dong_fang_liang","listener_name":"东方亮","tone":"惊讶","text":"东方亮？你就是那个……","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":89,"line_end":89,"text":"东方亮？你就是那个……"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_010","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_yan","speaker_name":"西门燕","listener":"dong_fang_liang","listener_name":"东方亮","tone":"撒娇","text":"听说你武功很厉害，是不是真的？","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":91,"line_end":91,"text":"听说你武功很厉害，是不是真的？"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_011","chapter":8,"speaker":"dong_fang_liang","speaker_name":"东方亮","listener":"xi_men_yan","listener_name":"西门燕","tone":"平淡","text":"江湖传闻，多有夸大。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":93,"line_end":93,"text":"江湖传闻，多有夸大。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_012","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_yan","speaker_name":"西门燕","listener":"dong_fang_liang","listener_name":"东方亮","tone":"好奇","text":"那这位姐姐呢？","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":95,"line_end":95,"text":"那这位姐姐呢？"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_013","chapter":8,"speaker":"lan_shui_ling","speaker_name":"蓝水灵","listener":"xi_men_yan","listener_name":"西门燕","tone":"平淡","text":"我姓蓝，姑娘叫我蓝姑娘便是。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":97,"line_end":97,"text":"我姓蓝，姑娘叫我蓝姑娘便是。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_014","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_yan","speaker_name":"西门燕","listener":"lan_shui_ling","listener_name":"蓝水灵","tone":"犹豫","text":"你……你怎么老和东方公子在一起？","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":120,"line_end":120,"text":"你……你怎么老和东方公子在一起？"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_015","chapter":8,"speaker":"lan_shui_ling","speaker_name":"蓝水灵","listener":"xi_men_yan","listener_name":"西门燕","tone":"惊讶","text":"我们同路而已。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":122,"line_end":122,"text":"我们同路而已。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_016","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_yan","speaker_name":"西门燕","listener":"xi_men_fu_ren","listener_name":"西门夫人","tone":"撒娇","text":"娘，我不要和她们一起走！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":124,"line_end":124,"text":"娘，我不要和她们一起走！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_017","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_fu_ren","speaker_name":"西门夫人","listener":"xi_men_yan","listener_name":"西门燕","tone":"庄重","text":"燕儿不可任性，多个朋友多条路。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":126,"line_end":126,"text":"燕儿不可任性，多个朋友多条路。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_018","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_yan","speaker_name":"西门燕","listener":"xi_men_fu_ren","listener_name":"西门夫人","tone":"愤怒","text":"娘！您怎老帮着外人！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":128,"line_end":128,"text":"娘！您怎老帮着外人！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_019","chapter":8,"speaker":"hong_xiao","speaker_name":"红绡","listener":"xi_men_fu_ren","listener_name":"西门夫人","tone":"恭敬","text":"夫人，路上似有动静。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":200,"line_end":200,"text":"夫人，路上似有动静。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_020","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_fu_ren","speaker_name":"西门夫人","listener":"hong_xiao","listener_name":"红绡","tone":"平静","text":"知道了，让大家小心。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":202,"line_end":202,"text":"知道了，让大家小心。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_021","chapter":8,"speaker":"bao_yi_xu","speaker_name":"鲍一虚","listener":"dong_fang_liang","listener_name":"东方亮","tone":"威胁","text":"姓蓝的小丫头，乖乖跟我们走！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":220,"line_end":220,"text":"姓蓝的小丫头，乖乖跟我们走！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_022","chapter":8,"speaker":"dong_fang_liang","speaker_name":"东方亮","listener":"bao_yi_xu","listener_name":"鲍一虚","tone":"冷峻","text":"想带人走，先问过在下。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":222,"line_end":222,"text":"想带人走，先问过在下。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_023","chapter":8,"speaker":"du_cheng_lin","speaker_name":"杜成林","listener":"dong_fang_liang","listener_name":"东方亮","tone":"愤怒","text":"小子不知死活，兄弟们上！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":224,"line_end":224,"text":"小子不知死活，兄弟们上！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_024","chapter":8,"speaker":"lan_shui_ling","speaker_name":"蓝水灵","listener":"dong_fang_liang","listener_name":"东方亮","tone":"急迫","text":"东方大哥，我来助你！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":226,"line_end":226,"text":"东方大哥，我来助你！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_025","chapter":8,"speaker":"dong_fang_liang","speaker_name":"东方亮","listener":"lan_shui_ling","listener_name":"蓝水灵","tone":"坚定","text":"蓝姑娘小心身后！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":228,"line_end":228,"text":"蓝姑娘小心身后！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_026","chapter":8,"speaker":"zhong_jiu_sheng","speaker_name":"钟九胜","listener":"lan_shui_ling","listener_name":"蓝水灵","tone":"咆哮","text":"小丫头乖乖受缚！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":260,"line_end":260,"text":"小丫头乖乖受缚！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_027","chapter":8,"speaker":"lan_shui_ling","speaker_name":"蓝水灵","listener":"zhong_jiu_sheng","listener_name":"钟九胜","tone":"愤怒","text":"做梦！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":262,"line_end":262,"text":"做梦！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_028","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_yan","speaker_name":"西门燕","listener":"xi_men_fu_ren","listener_name":"西门夫人","tone":"紧张","text":"娘，他们打起来了！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":265,"line_end":265,"text":"娘，他们打起来了！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_029","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_fu_ren","speaker_name":"西门夫人","listener":"xi_men_yan","listener_name":"西门燕","tone":"平静","text":"燕儿莫慌，有娘在。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":267,"line_end":267,"text":"燕儿莫慌，有娘在。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_030","chapter":8,"speaker":"hong_xiao","speaker_name":"红绡","listener":"zi_yu","listener_name":"紫玉","tone":"急迫","text":"紫玉姐姐，保护夫人！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":270,"line_end":270,"text":"紫玉姐姐，保护夫人！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_031","chapter":8,"speaker":"zi_yu","speaker_name":"紫玉","listener":"hong_xiao","listener_name":"红绡","tone":"坚定","text":"放心，有我。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":272,"line_end":272,"text":"放心，有我。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_032","chapter":8,"speaker":"bao_yi_xu","speaker_name":"鲍一虚","listener":"dong_fang_liang","listener_name":"东方亮","tone":"惊讶","text":"你……你这是什么剑法？","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":300,"line_end":300,"text":"你……你这是什么剑法？"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_033","chapter":8,"speaker":"dong_fang_liang","speaker_name":"东方亮","listener":"bao_yi_xu","listener_name":"鲍一虚","tone":"平淡","text":"家父所传，何足挂齿。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":302,"line_end":302,"text":"家父所传，何足挂齿。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_034","chapter":8,"speaker":"yu_zhao_xing","speaker_name":"余兆兴","listener":"du_cheng_lin","listener_name":"杜成林","tone":"慌张","text":"师兄，点子扎手，扯呼！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":320,"line_end":320,"text":"师兄，点子扎手，扯呼！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_035","chapter":8,"speaker":"du_cheng_lin","speaker_name":"杜成林","listener":"yu_zhao_xing","listener_name":"余兆兴","tone":"愤怒","text":"撤！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":322,"line_end":322,"text":"撤！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_036","chapter":8,"speaker":"lan_shui_ling","speaker_name":"蓝水灵","listener":"dong_fang_liang","listener_name":"东方亮","tone":"感激","text":"东方大哥，多亏有你。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":330,"line_end":330,"text":"东方大哥，多亏有你。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_037","chapter":8,"speaker":"dong_fang_liang","speaker_name":"东方亮","listener":"lan_shui_ling","listener_name":"蓝水灵","tone":"平淡","text":"举手之劳，蓝姑娘不必客气。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":332,"line_end":332,"text":"举手之劳，蓝姑娘不必客气。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_038","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_yan","speaker_name":"西门燕","listener":"dong_fang_liang","listener_name":"东方亮","tone":"惊讶","text":"东方公子好厉害！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":340,"line_end":340,"text":"东方公子好厉害！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_039","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_yan","speaker_name":"西门燕","listener":"lan_shui_ling","listener_name":"蓝水灵","tone":"犹豫","text":"蓝姑娘，你……你没事吧？","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":342,"line_end":342,"text":"蓝姑娘，你……你没事吧？"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_040","chapter":8,"speaker":"lan_shui_ling","speaker_name":"蓝水灵","listener":"xi_men_yan","listener_name":"西门燕","tone":"惊讶","text":"西门姑娘关心，我没事。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":344,"line_end":344,"text":"西门姑娘关心，我没事。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_041","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_fu_ren","speaker_name":"西门夫人","listener":"dong_fang_liang","listener_name":"东方亮","tone":"庄重","text":"东方公子武艺高强，老身佩服。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":360,"line_end":360,"text":"东方公子武艺高强，老身佩服。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_042","chapter":8,"speaker":"dong_fang_liang","speaker_name":"东方亮","listener":"xi_men_fu_ren","listener_name":"西门夫人","tone":"恭敬","text":"西门夫人谬赞。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":362,"line_end":362,"text":"西门夫人谬赞。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_043","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_yan","speaker_name":"西门燕","listener":"xi_men_fu_ren","listener_name":"西门夫人","tone":"撒娇","text":"娘，我们和东方公子他们一起走嘛！","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":380,"line_end":380,"text":"娘，我们和东方公子他们一起走嘛！"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_044","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_fu_ren","speaker_name":"西门夫人","listener":"xi_men_yan","listener_name":"西门燕","tone":"平淡","text":"娘自有分寸，燕儿莫多言。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":382,"line_end":382,"text":"娘自有分寸，燕儿莫多言。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_045","chapter":8,"speaker":"lan_shui_ling","speaker_name":"蓝水灵","listener":"xi_men_yan","listener_name":"西门燕","tone":"犹豫","text":"西门姑娘，前路凶险，还是结伴的好。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":400,"line_end":400,"text":"西门姑娘，前路凶险，还是结伴的好。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_046","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_yan","speaker_name":"西门燕","listener":"lan_shui_ling","listener_name":"蓝水灵","tone":"惊讶","text":"你……你愿意和我们同行？","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":402,"line_end":402,"text":"你……你愿意和我们同行？"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_047","chapter":8,"speaker":"lan_shui_ling","speaker_name":"蓝水灵","listener":"xi_men_yan","listener_name":"西门燕","tone":"平淡","text":"我一个人也是危险，何不互相照应。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":404,"line_end":404,"text":"我一个人也是危险，何不互相照应。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_048","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_yan","speaker_name":"西门燕","listener":"lan_shui_ling","listener_name":"蓝水灵","tone":"撒娇","text":"好嘛好嘛，我答应你啦。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":406,"line_end":406,"text":"好嘛好嘛，我答应你啦。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_049","chapter":8,"speaker":"xi_men_fu_ren","speaker_name":"西门夫人","listener":"lan_shui_ling","listener_name":"蓝水灵","tone":"感激","text":"蓝姑娘宽宏大量，老身代燕儿谢过。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":410,"line_end":410,"text":"蓝姑娘宽宏大量，老身代燕儿谢过。"}]},
    {"id":"dlg_08_050","chapter":8,"speaker":"lan_shui_ling","speaker_name":"蓝水灵","listener":"xi_men_fu_ren","listener_name":"西门夫人","tone":"恭敬","text":"夫人言重了，路见不平，本该相助。","source_refs":[{"chapter":8,"line_start":412,"line_end":412,"text":"夫人言重了，路见不平，本该相助。"}]}
  ],
